result.title: Team Names
result.content:
Hey guys!

Just a request for the presentation of your team, so that everybody can see who they are competing with. Your team should:

  1. Set up the correct country flag.

  2. Write your team name according to the expression <University Name #Number>: <Team Name> (without the angle brackets), for example: "Baltic University #2: Always The First".

Thanks, good luck & have fun!
